      "raw_text": "Attorney r. Nj. Stephens will\nleave for Chicago Friday to appear\nbefore the Interstate Commerce\ncommission in further hearing of\nthe Spokane rate case on July H..\nAn effort viii be made at that time\nto have the commission cause the\nrates to become effective as soon\nas possible. Members Of the rate\ncommittee of the chamber Of com\nmerce believe that all of the local\nrailroads will soon come to the new\nrates."
